AccountStatus.description:
Specifies the current primary status of an account. Possible values are:
 Enabled, 
 Dormant,
 Disable,
 Deleted,
 Pending, 
 Form.
 Pending, 
 Denied, 
 Review,
 Approve,
 ChargeOff,
 Active,
 PaymentPastDue,
 Bankruptcy,
 AuthorizationProhibited,
 InterestProhibited,
 Closed, Restricted.
